Package com.rb.nonbiz.testutils

Class MatcherEpsilons

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.testutils.MatcherEpsilons
public class MatcherEpsilons
extends java.lang.Object
Normally, our test matchers use 1e-8 (DEFAULT_EPSILON). However, sometimes we want to override the epsilons. This helps you accomplish that.

In the higher-level repos, see OrdersTest#testEpsilonsInfra for how this gets used. Also, see MatcherEpsilonsTest.
